  Rules: No font weight lighter than 400. Mono for all cryptographic/technical values only. Tight letter-spacing on headings. ALL CAPS + 0.08em spacing for section   
  labels.

  Spacing Scale

  4px grid: 4 В· 8 В· 12 В· 16 В· 20 В· 24 В· 32 В· 48 В· 64

  Card padding is always 32px. Input padding is 11px 16px. Modal padding is 32px.

  Radius

  - xs: 4px (small code blocks, tooltips)
  - sm: 8px (small cards, inputs)
  - md: 12px (cards, containers)
  - lg: 18px (buttons, message bubbles)
  - xl: 24px (large cards)
  - 2xl: 32px (app shell corners)
  - full: 9999px (badges, status dots)

  The Glass Effect

  THIS is the signature look. Every surface element:

  background: var(--surface-color);
  backdrop-filter: blur(40px) saturate(200%);
  -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(40px) saturate(200%);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
  box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);

  Plus a 1px top highlight on every card:
  /* pseudo-element ::before on cards */
  position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 1px;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(255,255,255,0.08), transparent);
  pointer-events: none;

  This creates that "edge-lit in the dark" premium look вҖ” like the UI is floating on glass shelves with a dim light from above.

  Shadows

  --shadow-sm:  0 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.2)
  --shadow-md:  0 8px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.3)
  --shadow-lg:  0 16px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.4)
  --shadow-xl:  0 24px 80px rgba(0,0,0,0.6)
  --shadow-accent: 0 4px 12px rgba(99,102,241,0.2)
  --shadow-accent-strong: 0 8px 24px rgba(99,102,241,0.4)

  In light mode, all shadow opacities are halved.

  Transitions

  Single cubic-bezier everywhere: cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1)
  - fast: 150ms (inputs, badges)
  - base: 300ms (buttons, hover states)
  - smooth: 500ms (view transitions, modals)

  This curve is "ease-out with a crisp snap" вҖ” feels responsive, never sluggish.

